title: #92Noon! Presidents Day - St Peter/Majka/Wilf/Rosas
description: Celebrating our MN sports Presidents on Presidents Day....Twins Prez Dave St Peter opens the show, Wild boss Matt Majka ends the first hour, Vikings Owner/President Mark Wilf begins the final hour, and Wolves POBO Gersson Rosas wraps the show! Football talkers mixed in between!
